        <head xml:id="gd-p1d57-Hd1e103">DISTINCTIO LVII.</head>
        <p xml:id="gd-p1d57-d1e106">GRATIANUS.</p>
        <p xml:id="gd-p1d57-d1e109">Item, qui in egritudine constitutus baptizatur, presbiter ordinari non debet.</p>
        <p xml:id="gd-p1d57-d1e112">Unde in Neocesariensi Concilio, [c. 12.] legitur:</p>
        <div xml:id="gd-p1d57-Dd1e115">
          <head xml:id="gd-p1d57-Hd1e117">C. I</head>
          <head xml:id="gd-p1d57-Hd1e120" type="question-title">. Non ordinetur presbiter, in egritudine constitutus
            baptizatur.</head>
          <p xml:id="gd-p1d57-d1e123">Si* quis in egritudine constitutus baptizatus fuerit,presbiter ordinari non debet, (non
            enim fides illius uoluntaria, sed ex necessitate est), nisi forte postea ipsius studium
            etfides probabilis fuerit, aut hominum raritas exegerit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
